This paper deals with data management in cloud systems, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the use of Mechanism Design, which is a subfield of Game Theory (cs.GT). Additionally, the paper discusses indexing and materialized views, which are common techniques used in databases (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses the optimization of queries, which is a common problem in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI).
